6T03:05:49.000Z","msg":"騎墻黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T06:21:58.000Z","msg":"呢啲先係有政治智慧<br />\n行一步 俾個獨立調查你平復民憤 <br />\n之後雙普選 自決果啲訴求自然會減弱<br />\n<br />\n如果乜都唔回應只會繼續滾雪球最後爆煲 which is exactly what 777 is doing"},{"pid":"3577935911fcd941d959b4c7c8f25a187a755faa","tid":1366402,"uid":190129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T06:24:07.000Z","msg":"食5大訴求2樣，  仲有721個彈未拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa6adaec5e9e275d5f5268cc219ea6860fb6cc35","tid":1366402,"uid":229835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T06:24:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/2166343906807690/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F2166343906807690%2F&d=AixoiqhHuTrv0%2F0Xa%2FX9x4hgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=e83b840f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/2166343906807690/</a><br />\n<br />\n值得睇呀<br />\n<br />\n【石永泰促成立獨立調查委員會】<br />\n【法官領導調查 甚至可證警隊清白】<br />\n<br />\n大律師公會前主席石永泰促請政府成立獨立調查委員會，認為是化解怨憤的一條出路。<br />\n<br />\n他相信在法官領導下，委員會不會只查一邊，甚至有助證明警隊清白。<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞 #石永泰 #獨立調查委員會 #衝突 #逃犯條例"},{"pid":"1c7d1870cac48480f4f517297eb99143fc9484ac","tid":1366402,"uid":263464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T06:25:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/29D0Qbi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F29D0Qbi.jpg&h=6f02eb51&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f8afdf8456eb2513afb63e0545a8b22e0f4eca5","tid":1366402,"uid":180851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eff639497253764462a4b7d488d6345f3affb41a","tid":1366402,"uid":211461,"like":1,"dislike":90,"score":-89,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:02:42.000Z","msg":"問心<br />\n香港人係唔係政府肯成立獨調委就收貨<br />\n一定唔會查死警察一邊 抗爭者都會查<br />\n到時會有黑警被釘 義士都會被釘埋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T06:30:25.000Z","msg":"清 你個良心去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點問心"},{"pid":"f8141a6afd35323d3bf38b6742202ce9b3f077e4","tid":1366402,"uid":107828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T06:32:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c31472506289927124fd908ab1137efe8ab1f0","tid":1366402,"uid":92166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T06:36:57.000Z","msg":"班商家唔係睇今日損失左幾多<br />\n而係班官，日柒日d行為都係撩得d市民更火，根本唔係&quot;處理&quot;緊，而係攪緊屎棍，連拉一派打一派呢d咁柒常見既手段都攪到一獲粥咁，整左元朗單野出黎<br />\n<br />\n做人又冇公關，一日一日咁過去，成個社會越黎越對立，越黎越爨，根本見唔到會完既跡象，唔完，咁係咪真係要解放軍入城，攬炒，商家佬就至撚驚呢味野<br />\n<br />\n商界係睇緊將來個結果，呢班官咁柒樣攪，將來損失已經可以預期好撚大<br />\n<br />\n所以咪叫佢唔識攪就咪撚攪，真係獲獲出黎見記者都好似攪屎棍，嫌d人唔夠嬲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc92c99222ec448376d8086cff50704da2c0744f","tid":1366402,"uid":144156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"74e5cd2a392dc1ed431ff81db8224560dee39187","tid":1366402,"uid":281754,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:08:50.000Z","msg":"選舉近，怪獸都會化為人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T06:45:17.000Z","msg":"直接證明有民主選舉重要性"},{"pid":"1671eaa871c9e69b686a20f96ea3872152da917e","tid":1366402,"uid":269743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eff639497253764462a4b7d488d6345f3affb41a","tid":1366402,"uid":211461,"like":1,"dislike":90,"score":-89,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:02:42.000Z","msg":"問心<br />\n香港人係唔係政府肯成立獨調委就收貨<br />\n一定唔會查死警察一邊 抗爭者都會查<br />\n到時會有黑警被釘 義士都會被釘埋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T06:50:13.000Z","msg":"義士不嬲都冇停止過被清算緊<br />\n但黑警仲un un腳"},{"pid":"8acc6f677af20421400622226172d7bbaf82d675","tid":1366402,"uid":97759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:02:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"548f044f99f32dc0709dfefce148d5a808b10ffa","tid":1366402,"uid":97759,"like":0,"dislik